snippet.title: WinKings - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
WinKings is a party game, which throws you in fantasy Vikings era. 
You can play with different characters such as:

Alessa - Woman at war! A true killing machine. 
Olaf - Passed Ninjas school! Needs seconds to stop enemies heart beat.
Gun - Nobody has seen his face before. He got mysterious reward from viking gods.
Einar - Veteran worrier. His axe has sacrificed many lives!

The goal is really easy - Win every battle!
Game can be played from 1 to 4 players.

https://www.facebook.com/winkingsgame/
